reviews.text: This small restaurant / take away is tucked right inside the arcade and you would not notice it normally. It is more akin to a fast food takeout and has a selection of Semi Japanese and American dishes. It is extremely popular during the lunch hour and there is always a wait here. I ordered their Angus beef burger with fries and a coke and the wait was about 8 minutes. The burger was great and nicely cooked. As it is tucked well inside the arcade, there are no views here. The prices here are also reasonable and they also have some happy hour specials.
Lots of space and seat. Nice food
Quite a spacious place with self service order kiosk...not bad for a Japanese beef rice for 65 bucks and a can of pop
Comfy environment. Food fair.

result.name: 板上

reviews.text: 白飯和湯雖可自添，但可惜沒有fill up, 而食物味道和份量ok.
等好耐，好慢，買餐加8蚊有多四隻一半的炸雞亦仔，點知唔記得買餐加，佢就冇得加返，重話而家出左單，就唔可以話唔買，冇啦啦比多成32蚊羅
意大利薄餅和烤羊肉飯不錯。有機會再嘗試牛肉漢堡和炸薯條。
好的餐廳。員工好有禮貌。
此間日本風的燒肉店位於中海日昇中心的商場地下，環境空間感充足，可以應付大量的食飯人潮，其餐飲質素達到中上水準，其烤肉烤魚均是十分新鮮，醬汁亦做得不錯，當中用木盒盛載的食品最有風味，但唯獨價錢已達$60元的水平，所以普遍在週末時候吃會較好，但平時返工吃飯的打工仔則會覺得這裡較貴。
